latestPosts.caption:
After a year of hard work, patience, sleepless nights and immense support from my loved ones, I bring you a piece of my heart, a dream, Becks Beauty Bar is here and is all yours to experience.
We look forward to your love, support and blessings 💗
latestPosts.alt: Photo shared by BECKS on May 16, 2023 tagging @becksbeautybar_.

latestPosts.caption:
Dreams do come true! 💖 Today, I am beyond excited to announce the launch of my very own beauty brand, a dream that started way back when I used to play with my mother’s makeup. Starting with our first line of fabulous press-on nails, we’re ready to bring a touch of magic to your beauty routine. ✨

I owe this milestone to a special angel who has been my guiding light and to my incredible friends and family who have supported me every step of the way. Thank you for believing in me and making this dream a reality. Let’s make beauty dreams come true together! 💅🏼🌟

#DreamComeTrue #BeautyBrand #Grateful #PressOnNails #NewBeginnings #comingsoon
